# https://stgermain.ebsi.umontreal.ca/miron/Oiseau
<https://stgermain.ebsi.umontreal.ca/miron/Oiseau> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
